Step 1. Open your C compiler or IDE and create a new file to write the code.
Step 2. Copy the code provided into your file and save it with a .c extension.
Step 3. Compile the code to make sure it has no errors.
Step 4. Run the program to start the game.
5. The game will display the 3x3 game board and prompt you to enter the row and column for your mark.
